Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.92,0:01:43.23,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Death?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.23,0:01:44.66,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,My death?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.96,0:01:56.90,Default,Yellow,0000,0000,0000,,Sleigh Beggies are treasures, in that you \Ncreate an unending supply of magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.25,0:01:59.62,Default,Yellow,0000,0000,0000,,but your bodies are very fragile.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.37,0:02:04.79,Default,Yellow,0000,0000,0000,,Just being alive, you relentlessly \Nabsorb and generate magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.53,0:02:08.31,Default,Yellow,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, your body will buckle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.85,0:02:11.31,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,You're well-versed in the matter, Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.31,0:02:11.77,Default,Yellow,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:17.19,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,He keeps you alive without taking any \Nmeasures to help you out of danger,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.19,0:02:19.57,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,just to satiate his own curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.57,0:02:27.86,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,That dizziness...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.80,0:02:33.00,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,Chise-kun, he has no feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:38.72,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,You can't expect human kindness \Nfrom a sham of a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.44,0:02:42.90,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,He bought you with money and \Ntied you down with that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.59,0:02:45.59,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,He has a tracking spell on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.50,0:02:47.85,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,You must have suffered.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:55.61,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,We'll set you free.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:09.79,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Ariel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.90,0:03:11.95,Default,Yellow,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.80,0:03:18.13,Default,King Mop,0000,0000,0000,,This place is our territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:21.13,Default,King Mop,0000,0000,0000,,I won't have sorcerers \Nwandering around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.32,0:03:23.00,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Ariel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:27.43,Default,Ariel,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm fine, as long as \NI'm not touching metal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:28.98,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.98,0:03:30.85,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to be set free?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:33.87,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,From what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:38.44,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,If you mean from Elias, you \Nprobably wouldn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.00,0:03:43.36,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he was lying, he was the \Nonly one to ever call me family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:47.60,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care whether you were \Nlying or telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.51,0:03:51.48,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,He was the first person to value me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.87,0:03:56.63,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,So until Elias lets go of my hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:03:59.92,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I belong to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:07.50,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,Alice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:10.23,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.80,0:04:12.01,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,I am shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:15.77,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,I lurk in the shadows of thorns.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.16,0:04:19.48,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,I am what you call the Pilum Murialis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:27.68,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Chise?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:28.55,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:29.70,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Can I see your wound?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:30.89,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,My wound?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.89,0:04:32.28,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,That was reckless of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:34.67,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:38.03,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,You humans don't last very \Nlong once you're injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:39.57,Default,Ariel,0000,0000,0000,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.57,0:04:41.45,Default,Ariel,0000,0000,0000,,You're a pale shadow of a shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:42.90,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Chise was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.90,0:04:44.27,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,What could I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:51.45,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Its bonds are coming loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:54.42,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Chise, I'll take care of things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:56.06,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the cleansing to you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:57.27,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.72,0:04:59.06,Default,King Mop,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:00.35,Default,Bernie,0000,0000,0000,,King!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.17,0:05:04.33,Default,Ariel,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:06.32,Default,Ariel,0000,0000,0000,,Chise and I are going to handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:12.41,Default,King Mop,0000,0000,0000,,It's the final duty of the king to \Nsee that the corruption is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:13.99,Default,King Mop,0000,0000,0000,,Is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.16,0:05:59.06,Default,Ariel,0000,0000,0000,,Chise!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.14,0:06:00.15,Default,Ariel,0000,0000,0000,,Chise!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:01.39,Default,Ariel,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:03.38,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.66,0:06:05.69,Default,King Mop,0000,0000,0000,,A tavern from long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:07.47,Default,King Mop,0000,0000,0000,,A place to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:10.32,Default,Left,0000,0000,0000,,The neighboring town was beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:12.54,Default,Right,0000,0000,0000,,I heard there are a lot of \Nbeautiful women there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:13.76,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I can see through myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:17.51,Default,Ariel,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we're inside \Nthe corruption's memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:21.56,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,That man...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.94,0:06:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:38.53,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you the wandering sorcerer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.53,0:06:45.62,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.27,0:06:48.38,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,Are you surprised that I'm so small?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:50.71,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,Did you need some help?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.71,0:06:52.17,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.16,0:06:57.01,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,People everywhere depend \Non me when I'm traveling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:06:58.73,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,Bad harvests?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:01.05,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to win a special lady's attention?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:05.01,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,No, my wife's always been frail.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:07.58,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,She always ends up bedridden.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:11.07,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I want her to become healthier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:14.19,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have medicine or \Nanything that'll help?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:18.50,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,You must care a lot about your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:19.86,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:21.81,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,That was a fast reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:24.20,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,You're an embarrassing man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:31.12,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,May I see your wife in person?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.56,0:07:33.37,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:34.66,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Come soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:44.25,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,He's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.09,0:07:48.21,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.50,0:07:49.96,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,Get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:51.90,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go talk to your husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.29,0:07:53.13,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:55.33,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:08:00.58,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,So, how is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:02.41,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Tim?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.78,0:08:03.65,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Tim.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.56,0:08:08.24,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Tim?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:12.20,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think she'll get \Nany better than she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:14.62,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,She won't last more than a few years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:16.40,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,She was born that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.77,0:08:17.72,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.04,0:08:19.37,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.78,0:08:26.39,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mina couldn't even play \Noutside as a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.39,0:08:29.47,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,She's hard-working in spirit, but she \Ncan't do much because of her health!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.47,0:08:31.17,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,She deserves better!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:33.80,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do anything for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:34.88,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.88,0:08:37.28,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't bear to see her die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.02,0:08:42.40,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,Does your wife like cats?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.86,0:08:44.83,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Cats?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:47.92,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:49.55,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:51.46,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,That's perfect, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:56.42,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard that cats have nine lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:02.47,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,More rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.88,0:09:07.35,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Is it just me, or are there \Nlots of rats lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:10.24,Default,C,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose the cats aren't doing their jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:11.86,Default,C,0000,0000,0000,,Mina.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:14.64,Default,C,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you're well\Nenough to be up and about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.02,0:09:20.57,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the weather's nice today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:23.33,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Matthew?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:26.37,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I went to bring him a meal, \Nbut he wasn't in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:30.17,Default,<_<,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's out meeting a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.91,0:09:33.33,Default,◎＿◎,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:37.93,Default,◎＿◎,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Everyone knows Matthew's all about Mina.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.96,0:09:38.77,Default,C,0000,0000,0000,,I saw him go into the forest with an axe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I was just joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.31,0:09:40.23,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,The forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:53.41,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Matthew!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:55.27,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Matthew!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.61,0:10:05.60,Default,Ariel,0000,0000,0000,,Chise, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:07.68,Default,Ariel,0000,0000,0000,,You look really pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.25,0:10:11.63,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I have a really bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.59,0:10:30.72,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,A shed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.72,0:10:33.06,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Was there always a shed here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:41.78,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:45.27,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What's that Matthew up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.97,0:10:49.16,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Matthew?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.55,0:10:50.38,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.69,0:10:51.73,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Matthew.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.14,0:10:54.15,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.37,0:10:58.88,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.19,0:11:04.35,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Matthew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.61,0:11:27.66,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Mina.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.35,0:11:40.46,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you're doing well today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:43.24,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.24,0:11:45.50,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I just finished making this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:48.71,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It's your medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.71,0:11:50.09,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.51,0:11:52.44,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Matthew, what are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.11,0:11:54.38,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:57.43,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Remember we had a sorcerer see you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.74,0:12:03.04,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,He told me that this potion \Nwould make you better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.67,0:12:05.79,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Th-These cats...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.25,0:12:07.63,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Where did these cats come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.63,0:12:09.88,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,They're ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.88,0:12:12.83,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,They say cats have nine lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:14.92,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:18.76,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,He said I could make you \Nmedicine out of the cats' lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:23.24,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,How unfair is it that these \Nbeasts have so many lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:24.15,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Matthew!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.15,0:12:25.76,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what happened to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.17,0:12:28.37,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,How could you do such a terrible thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:31.48,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't the kind of \Nperson who could do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.90,0:12:33.60,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:41.06,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It's for your sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.04,0:12:44.31,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Matthew...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:48.11,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.84,0:12:51.86,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.42,0:12:56.70,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,Drink that, and you'll go from \Nbeing weak to able-bodied.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:13:00.35,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,You might even be able to live forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.35,0:13:01.60,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.16,0:13:03.73,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What have you done to Matthew?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:07.38,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,I just had him trust me a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:12.05,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, it's a magnificent drug.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.98,0:13:14.10,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.09,0:13:18.52,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,Be a mouse for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:35.49,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Mina, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:37.84,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,He said it only hurts in the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:40.07,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Mina.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:42.34,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be well after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:48.30,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.75,0:13:49.39,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:54.18,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Mat... thew...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:22.62,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear, it failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:24.46,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,She lost her form.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.08,0:14:28.44,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose beasts are just beasts after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:30.97,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,They're easier to process than humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:33.68,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess their strong instincts \Nmeans they have strong curses, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.42,0:14:37.61,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I'll have to go back to \Nfiguring out how to condense souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:40.90,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the valuable \Nresearch data, Mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:44.03,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:46.74,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:48.98,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Mina...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.53,0:14:50.43,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Mina...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:51.25,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Mina...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.81,0:14:53.38,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Mina?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.38,0:14:55.46,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops, he broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.46,0:14:57.78,Default,Sophie from Howl's,0000,0000,0000,,Love's amazing, huh, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.09,0:14:59.13,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.26,0:15:00.14,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:01.01,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.33,0:15:13.26,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.55,0:15:17.22,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:22.72,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I still need more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.73,0:15:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:24.90,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,More,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:25.88,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:27.73,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I need to gather more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:31.43,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I need to gather... more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.32,0:15:36.28,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Tim.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:38.42,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.17,0:15:42.45,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Your precious Mina is in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.97,0:15:45.05,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.51,0:15:46.09,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:58.85,Default,Tiny Timmy,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't human anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:00.55,Default,Tiny Timmy,0000,0000,0000,,You're a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.92,0:16:04.52,Default,Tiny Timmy,0000,0000,0000,,You were deceived by a demon into \Nbecoming a pitiful demon yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.26,0:16:07.90,Default,Tiny Timmy,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you live,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:10.57,Default,Tiny Timmy,0000,0000,0000,,and I can't let you die in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.12,0:16:13.33,Default,Tiny Timmy,0000,0000,0000,,I was chosen to be the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:16.27,Default,Tiny Timmy,0000,0000,0000,,I also do this for those who died.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.42,0:16:21.45,Magus-Internal/narrator,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Mina...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.09,0:16:25.14,Magus-Internal/narrator,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Mina...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.93,0:16:28.88,Magus-Internal/narrator,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Mina...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:33.24,Magus-Internal/narrator,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Mina?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.52,0:16:36.92,Magus-Internal/narrator,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so lonely without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.19,0:16:39.15,Magus-Internal/narrator,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Mina...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.03,0:16:41.03,Magus-Internal/narrator,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Mina...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.79,0:16:50.78,Default,King Mop,0000,0000,0000,,Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:58.31,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I've made you see something\N terrible, haven't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.92,0:17:03.17,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I only intended to have you erase us,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.22,0:17:06.41,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,but you have a powerful gift of sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.62,0:17:08.58,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.48,0:17:17.17,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "erase"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.56,0:17:19.03,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I mean what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.58,0:17:21.17,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Make us not exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:27.65,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,The souls of all living\Nthings are part of a cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:34.14,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,But Matthew and I have \Nforgotten how to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:35.94,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,As have the cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:37.87,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,The cats?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.26,0:17:41.61,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,The souls of the cats who bore \Na curse from their murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:47.15,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,We've all forgotten how to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.94,0:17:52.05,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,So, I want you to erase us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.05,0:17:52.91,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.60,0:17:55.91,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,You were only deceived.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.91,0:17:57.87,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,You don't deserve to be erased!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.96,0:18:00.89,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You must.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.67,0:18:02.59,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.45,0:18:07.47,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,All that waits for us if we lose our chance \Nnow is an even more painful, endless void.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:10.95,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only who can help us right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.74,0:18:14.51,Default,King Mop,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lead the way, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.93,0:18:15.94,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,King.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:18.58,Default,King Mop,0000,0000,0000,,This is my ninth life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.98,0:18:21.05,Default,King Mop,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be returning soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:26.25,Default,King Mop,0000,0000,0000,,I should be able to guide \Nyou to where you belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:27.08,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:28.70,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,You can't! That girl will be sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:31.14,Default,King Mop,0000,0000,0000,,Death is always sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:34.91,Default,King Mop,0000,0000,0000,,Sooner or later, it comes to all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.32,0:18:38.51,Default,King Mop,0000,0000,0000,,The last king, and the one before,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.51,0:18:42.36,Default,King Mop,0000,0000,0000,,all sacrificed their souls\Nto hold off the corruption.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:48.11,Default,King Mop,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to that, being \Na guide isn't difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.43,0:18:51.10,Default,King Mop,0000,0000,0000,,I have good memories with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:56.28,Default,King Mop,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.15,0:19:01.25,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.51,0:19:06.71,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.45,0:19:11.23,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.23,0:19:17.76,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Ariel, with your power, with the \Nwind to carry seeds far away...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.20,0:19:23.43,Default,Ariel,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:26.28,Default,Ariel,0000,0000,0000,,Seed to soil, flower to seed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.28,0:19:28.77,Default,Ariel,0000,0000,0000,,That is the pact of the soil and the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.77,0:19:31.98,Default,Ariel,0000,0000,0000,,Those whose time is to return, to \Nthe place where they must return.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.98,0:19:35.76,Default,Ariel,0000,0000,0000,,Humans sure are silly and \Nclever. You're amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:40.01,Default,Ariel,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we can never get enough of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:47.89,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,We won't erase you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.89,0:19:49.04,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:50.34,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,She'll take you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.28,0:19:53.14,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,So picture it in your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.84,0:19:57.77,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Dandelions, sending their \Nseeds off into the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.47,0:20:03.98,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,There, they set root and sprout.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.92,0:20:08.80,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,The wind blows toward where you need to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:20:58.93,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Matthew!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.23,0:21:02.20,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Mina!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.90,0:21:06.94,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Matthew!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.99,0:21:15.70,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Mina.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:18.25,Default,Cat Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.68,0:21:19.75,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Matthew.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.46,0:21:22.47,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Matthew.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.35,0:21:28.74,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Chise,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.76,0:21:31.64,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,the little mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:37.52,Default,Cat Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I pray that you don't come\N here any time soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.41,0:21:59.82,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I was an unnecessary child.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.82,0:22:03.98,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,No one wanted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.98,0:22:08.01,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I was kicked out, and I wandered\Nendlessly. And finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.01,0:22:16.95,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I might've found a perch.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.27,0:22:22.52,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,When am I going to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.86,0:24:00.47,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,The guiding of souls came at a great cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.47,0:24:04.75,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,A girl, on the brink of sleep, \Nand a mage watching over her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.75,0:24:07.04,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,The two were met by...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.04,0:24:09.68,Default,Jellybra,0000,0000,0000,,Would you introduce me to your wife?
